'''''Winter Olympics''''' is a [[sports video game]] published in 1986 by [[Tynesoft]] for the [[Atari 8-bit computers]], [[Commodore 16]], [[Commodore Plus/4]], and [[MSX]].

==Gameplay==
The game features six events: [[Speed skating at the Winter Olympics|speed skating]], [[Ski jumping at the Winter Olympics|ski jump]], [[Bobsleigh at the Winter Olympics|bobsleigh]], [[Alpine skiing at the Winter Olympics|alpine skiing]] ([[Slalom skiing|slalom]] and downhill), and [[Curling at the Winter Olympics|curling]] (not available in the Atari version).<ref name="CUser"/><ref name="ASM"/>

